      "source": "251系",
      "translation": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{freetrain-tomy-train-20050531-jre251o}.description",
      "source": "1990年,伊豆への行楽用に登場した特急型電車。見晴らしの良いハイデッカーとダブルデッカーの豪華な編成。",
      "translation": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{freetrain-tomy-train-20051005-jreE233}.name",
      "source": "中央線(快速)",
      "translation": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{freetrain-tomy-train-20051005-jreE233}.company",
